    "title": {
      "rendered": "11 Responsively Designed Nonprofit Websites to Study and Learn From"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/nonprofits-must-us-responsive-design.gif\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-15603\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"nonprofits-must-us-responsive-design\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/nonprofits-must-us-responsive-design-300x300.gif?resize=300%2C300\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/nonprofits-must-us-responsive-design.gif?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/nonprofits-must-us-responsive-design.gif?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/nonprofits-must-us-responsive-design.gif?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/nonprofits-must-us-responsive-design.gif?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>With <a href=\"http://mashable.com/2014/02/24/facebook-mobile-traffic/\">51% of Facebook&#8217;s referral traffic</a> now coming from mobile and more than <a href=\"http://expandedramblings.com/index.php/march-2013-by-the-numbers-a-few-amazing-twitter-stats/\">two-third&#8217;s of Twitter users</a> being mobile, many nonprofits are finally starting to come to the realization that their social media campaigns are doomed unless they <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How-To-Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460/ref=bxgy_cc_b_img_a\">embrace a mobile-first approach</a>\u00a0to online communications and fundraising. Your nonprofit must now assume that the majority of website and blog content you share on social networks is being read on a mobile device and if that content is not mobile compatible, then any attempt to inspire a followerer or fan to donate or get more involved will fail.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The easiest way to ensure that your website and blog are mobile compatible is to <a href=\"http://www.bureauforgood.com/\">embrace responsive design</a>. As a follow-up list from last year&#8217;s <a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/2013/04/07/nonprofitresponsivedesign/\">7 Responsively Designed Nonprofit Websites to Study and Learn From</a>, below is a new selection of 11 exceptional, responsively designed nonprofit websites. Pay particular attention Heifer International. Their new site is <em>gorgeous</em>. Hopefully, your nonprofit has a new website on your To Do List for 2014-15 and you can study and learn from the websites listed below. Be sure to experience each of them on a desktop, tablet, and smartphone \u2013\u00a0and if possible, on two new screens we&#8217;ll be paying more attention to and designing for in the coming years\u00a0\u2013\u00a0a smartwatch and smart TV.</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">1. Families Against Mandatory Minimums (FAMM)<br />\n<a href=\"http://famm.org/\">famm.org</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://famm.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15597\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"famm responsive\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/famm-responsive.png?resize=600%2C300\" width=\"600\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/famm-responsive.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/famm-responsive.png?resize=300%2C150&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">2. Gates Foundation<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.gatesfoundation.org/\">gatesfoundation.org</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.gatesfoundation.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15592\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"gates foundation responsive\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/gates-foundation-responsive.png?resize=600%2C328\" width=\"600\" height=\"328\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/gates-foundation-responsive.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/gates-foundation-responsive.png?resize=300%2C164&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">3.\u00a0Gay &amp; Lesbian Alliance Against Defamation (Glaad)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.glaad.org/\">glaad.org</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.glaad.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15588\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"glaad responsive\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/glaad-responsive.png?resize=600%2C295\" width=\"600\" height=\"295\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/glaad-responsive.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/glaad-responsive.png?resize=300%2C147&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">4. Heifer International<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.heifer.org/\">heifer.org</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.heifer.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15580\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Heifer International Responsive\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Heifer-International-Responsive.png?resize=600%2C293\" width=\"600\" height=\"293\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Heifer-International-Responsive.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Heifer-International-Responsive.png?resize=300%2C146&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">5. National Campaign to Prevent Teen<br />\nand Unplanned Pregnancy<br />\n<a href=\"http://thenationalcampaign.org/\">thenationalcampaign.org</a></h2>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://thenationalcampaign.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15594\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"national campaign responsive\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/national-campaign-responsive.png?resize=600%2C290\" width=\"600\" height=\"290\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/national-campaign-responsive.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/national-campaign-responsive.png?resize=300%2C145&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></h2>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">6. Nature Conservancy<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nature.org/\">nature.org</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.nature.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15582\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"nature conservancy responsive\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/nature-conservancy-responsive.png?resize=600%2C294\" width=\"600\" height=\"294\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/nature-conservancy-responsive.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/nature-conservancy-responsive.png?resize=300%2C147&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">7. Oxfam America<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.oxfamamerica.org/\">oxfamamerica.org</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.oxfamamerica.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15584\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"oxfam america responsive\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/oxfam-america-responsive.png?resize=600%2C272\" width=\"600\" height=\"272\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/oxfam-america-responsive.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/oxfam-america-responsive.png?resize=300%2C136&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">8. People for the Ethical Treatment of Animals<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.peta.org/\">peta.org</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.peta.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15578\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Peta Responsive\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Peta-Responsive.png?resize=600%2C342\" width=\"600\" height=\"342\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Peta-Responsive.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Peta-Responsive.png?resize=300%2C171&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">9. Pew Research Center<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.pewresearch.org/\">pewresearch.org</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.pewresearch.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15586\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"pew research center responsiv e\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/pew-research-center-responsiv-e.png?resize=600%2C360\" width=\"600\" height=\"360\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/pew-research-center-responsiv-e.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/pew-research-center-responsiv-e.png?resize=300%2C180&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">10.\u00a0Rijksmuseum<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rijksmuseum.nl\">rijksmuseum.nl</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.rijksmuseum.nl\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15590\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"rijksmuseum responsive\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/rijksmuseum-responsive.png?resize=600%2C271\" width=\"600\" height=\"271\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/rijksmuseum-responsive.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/rijksmuseum-responsive.png?resize=300%2C135&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">11. Wilderness Society<br />\n<a href=\"http://wilderness.org/\">wilderness.org</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://wilderness.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15599\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"wilderness society responsive\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/wilderness-society-responsive.png?resize=600%2C321\" width=\"600\" height=\"321\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/wilderness-society-responsive.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/wilderness-society-responsive.png?resize=300%2C160&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n",
